comments: Towns (MIN) and Adebayo (MIA) engage and disengage off ball without affecting the other's FOM.
[Observable in enhanced video] Waiters (MIA) is in the lane for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Adebayo (MIA) briefly places his hand around Towns' (MIN) right leg but does not affect his ability to get to the rebound.
Wiggins (MIN) makes marginal contact with Waiters' (MIA) side after his gather.
Towns (MIN) delivers contact to Dragic's (MIA) side and left leg as he sets the pick, affecting Dragic's ability to defend.
RLB shows Saric (MIN) makes clean contact with the ball before making marginal contact with Dragic's (MIA) side after he picks up his dribble.
Jones (MIN) makes contact with the ball and any contact to Dragic's (MIA) hand is considered incidental.
[Observable in enhanced video] RLB shows Dragic (MIA) hops consecutively on the same foot he gathered on.
Wade (MIA) cleanly blocks Saric's (MIN) jump shot attempt.
Winslow (MIA) makes marginal body contact with Bates-Diop (MIN) before cleanly blocking his shot attempt near the rim.

The crew communicated with the Replay Center to determine if the ball made contact with the rim during Bates-Diop's (MIN) shot attempt. After review, the ruling on the floor of a 24 second violation was confirmed.

Winslow (MIA) makes slight contact with his elbow to the side of Bates-Diop's (MIN) head/neck area during rebounding. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in Bates-Diop's (MIN) path and does not deliver the contact.
Wiggins (MIN) makes contact with Waiters' (MIA) right elbow during his shooting motion that affects his jump shot attempt.
Saric (MIN) makes marginal contact with Winslow (MIA) during rebounding.
LAR shows Wade (MIA) cleanly strips Towns (MIN) of the ball.
RAR shows Jones (MIN) makes clean contact with the ball after Wade's (MIA) gather.
Waiters (MIA) briefly has his arms around Bates-Diop's (MIN) midsection before correcting.
Winslow (MIA) engages and disengages with Wiggins (MIN) without affecting his FOM during the inbound.
Adebayo (MIA) and Towns (MIN) engage and disengage off ball without affecting the other's FOM during the inbound.
Winslow (MIA) commits the take foul on Jones (MIN).
Johnson (MIA) and Jones (MIN) engage during the inbound.  When Johnson releases, Jones falls to the floor on his own.
Waiters (MIA) commits the take foul on Bates-Diop (MIN).
Wiggins (MIN) briefly has his hands on Waiters' (MIA) hips before correcting during the inbound.
Adebayo (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in Okogie's (MIN) path and does not deliver the contact.
